<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VITAS Trading System - Test Email</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 20px; 
            background-color: #f5f5f5; 
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            background: white; 
            border-radius: 10px; 
            overflow: hidden; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); 
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2E8B57, #1B5E20); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .header h1 { 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 24px; 
        }
        .content { 
            padding: 20px; 
        }
        .success { 
            background: #E8F5E8; 
            padding: 15px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            margin: 20px 0; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .success h3 { 
            margin: 0 0 10px 0; 
            color: #2E8B57; 
        }
        .config { 
            background: #f8f9fa; 
            padding: 15px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            margin: 20px 0; 
        }
        .config h4 { 
            margin: 0 0 10px 0; 
            color: #1976D2; 
        }
        .config-item { 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
            margin: 5px 0; 
            padding: 5px 0; 
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; 
        }
        .footer { 
            margin-top: 30px; 
            padding: 20px; 
            background: #f8f9fa; 
            text-align: center; 
            font-size: 12px; 
            color: #666; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ¯ VITAS Trading System</h1>
            <p>Email Configuration Test</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="success">
                <h3>âœ… Email Configuration Working!</h3>
                <p>Your email notifications are properly configured and working with @nestjs-modules/mailer.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="config">
                <h4>ðŸ“Š Configuration Details:</h4>
                <div class="config-item">
                    <span>SMTP Host:</span>
                    <strong>{{smtpHost}}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="config-item">
                    <span>SMTP Port:</span>
                    <strong>{{smtpPort}}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="config-item">
                    <span>SMTP Secure:</span>
                    <strong>{{smtpSecure}}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="config-item">
                    <span>From:</span>
                    <strong>{{from}}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="config-item">
                    <span>To:</span>
                    <strong>{{to}}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="config-item">
                    <span>Generated:</span>
                    <strong>{{generatedAt}}</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>You will now receive trading alerts, daily summaries, and risk warnings from the VITAS Trading System.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Generated at: {{generatedAt}}</p>
            <p>This is a test email from your VITAS Trading System.</p>
            <p><strong>VITAS Trading System</strong> - Your AI Trading Assistant</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
